{
  "name": "坑窑",
  "icon": "pyrotech:kiln_pit",
  "category": "adapt",
  "pages": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "为了使用$(item)坑窑$()你需要一个$(item)坑窑$()方块，一个$(item)稻草$()制成的$(item)稻草捆$()，三个$(thing)原木$()以及一个$(l:appendix/ignition)点火装置$()。$(p)两个$(item)干燥的植物纤维$()可以被绑在一起来做$(item)稻草$()。"
    },
    {
      "type": "crafting",
      "recipe": "pyrotech:tech/basic/kiln_pit",
      "recipe2": "pyrotech:straw"
    },
    {
      "type": "rrr_crude_drying_recipe_drying_recipe_stone_oven_recipe",
      "crude_recipe": "pyrotech:straw",
      "recipe": "pyrotech:crude_drying_rack/straw",
      "stone_oven_recipe": "pyrotech:drying_rack/crude_drying_rack/straw"
    },
    {
      "type": "crafting",
      "recipe": "pyrotech:thatch",
      "text": "$(info_cn) $(item)稻草$()也可以通过晾干$(item)小麦$()来获得。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "使用$(item)坑窑$()需要以下几步：$(p)  $(l:adapt/pit_kiln#step_1)1. 放置坑窑$(/l)$(br)  $(l:adapt/pit_kiln#step_2)2. 添加原料$(/l)$(br)  $(l:adapt/pit_kiln#step_3)3. 放稻草捆$(/l)$(br)  $(l:adapt/pit_kiln#step_4)4. 添加原木$(/l)$(br)  $(l:adapt/pit_kiln#step_5)5. 点燃！$(/l)$(br)  $(l:adapt/pit_kiln#step_6)6. 等待……$(/l)$(p)你右边所看到的就是搭建$(item)坑窑$()的图示，后面的几页有更加详细的介绍。"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_kiln_00.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "title": "1. 放置坑窑",
      "anchor": "step_1",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_kiln_01.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "首先，挖个洞，把你的$(item)坑窑$()放在底部。$(p)$(info_cn) $(item)坑窑$()必须用泥土把底部和旁边的四个面包围，不能有易燃物质，上面需要裸露！"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "title": "2. 添加原料",
      "anchor": "step_2",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_kiln_02.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "然后，从上方添加你的原料到$(item)坑窑$()里。$(p)$(info_cn) $(item)坑窑$()一次只能烧制一个物品。$(p)$(warning_cn) 请注意，在2，3，4步的插图中，有两个放在$(item)坑窑$()旁边的$(item)草方块$()被移除了 - 移除它们只是为了让你看的更清晰，它们任然是需要的！"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "title": "3. 放稻草捆",
      "anchor": "step_3",
      "text": " 接着，放入$(item)稻草捆$()。",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_kiln_03.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "title": "4. 添加原木",
      "anchor": "step_4",
      "text": " 接下来，放入$(thing)原木$()。",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_kiln_04.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "title": "5. 点燃",
      "anchor": "step_5",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_burn_01.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "之后用任何$(l:appendix/ignition)点火装置$()来点燃它。$(p)$(info_cn) 不像$(thing)碳窑$()，$(item)坑窑$()在烧制时上边需要裸露。"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "title": "6. 等待",
      "anchor": "step_6",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_kiln_05.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "最后，等着。$(p)$(info_cn) 当$(item)坑窑$()烧制时，它会一直保持上方的火焰。$(p)$(warning_cn) 如果$(item)坑窑$()暴露在雨中，那么这次加工将会失败！"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "images": [
        "pyrotech:textures/gui/book/illustration/pit_kiln_06.png"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "当$(item)坑窑$()上方的火焰终于熄灭，在灰烬中挑选你的成品。$(p)$(warning_cn) 因为使用$(item)坑窑$()的环境恶劣，所以有一定的几率会导致失败。"
    },
    {
      "type": "relations",
      "entries": [
        "adapt/plant_fibers_dried",
        "adapt/twine",
        "adapt/drying_rack",
        "innovate/stone_oven",
        "bloom/refractory_oven",
        "appendix/ignition"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
